What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Fruit Brandy Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Fruit Brandy Market

Global fruit brandy market is expected to gain market growth in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research analyses the market to account from USD 23.9 billion in 2020 to USD 28.0 billion by 2028 growing at a CAGR of 2.0% in the above-mentioned forecast period.

Fruit brandy is a beverage produced by fermenting and fruit juices,distilling wine, and mashes and contains alcoholic content. The inclusion of antioxidant, antibacterial and polyphenolic compounds within the drink provides several health benefits to the consumers such as improving immunity against heart disease, cancer, cold and cough. It is basically consumed in cocktails and cooking related procedures for flavoring.

The major growing factor driving the growth of the market is the rise in consumers’ consumption of cocktails and the food products flavored by the fruit brandy. Furthermore, the advantages of its consumption such as digestive health benefits, improved immunity and resistance against heart diseases and cancer are expected to heighten the overall demand for fruit brandy market over the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. The rise in the health-conscious and organic product consuming population serve as foremost drivers for the fruit brandy market at a global level. However, the presence of bitterness in taste of the fruit brandy is projected to act as a restraint towards the growth of the market, whereas the high alcohol content in the product and rigid regulatory policies can challenge the growth of the fruit brandy market.

Moreover, the rise in the research and development efforts and rise in the plant-based medicines are expected to further generate new opportunities for the fruit brandy market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

